install - The installation script got from systemimager website, don't have
	to call this directly

download-packages.sh - call ./install with some other parameters. Its purpose
	is to download packages from systemimager website

steps:
1: ./download-packages.sh
2: ./packages-install.sh
3: ./image-server-steps.sh

To fix the MBR issue, you may want to call grub-install /dev/sda **ON THE SECONDARY HEAD NODE** (and don't forget to do chroot before then)
